  <brief_title>Elobixibat Colonic Motor Function Study</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Single Center, Placebo-controlled Trial to Evaluate the Effects of Elobixibat in Colonic Motor Functions in Patients With Chronic Idiopathic Constipation</official_title>
  <sponsors>
