  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized trial of 36 otherwise healthy patients with chronic idiopathic
      constipation. The purpose of the study is to compare the effects of daily single-dose oral
      elobixibat and placebo for 7 days on colonic motor effects.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
